<br>
Since that time what we do as a group, all casters, healers and everyone but the MT go to the left corner of the gallows (looking at the platform from where you enter). The MT goes to the middle of the benches. Since the others are further away, the mobs all attack the MT first. It also helps if the MT sits to start with to guarantee aggro. <br>
<br>
Once the MT has gained aggro we then move in next to him so that if one of us takes aggro during the fight for any reason, the MT doesn't have to move to get aggro back.<br>
<br>
Using this strategy for placement, we have not lost a trial since and have managed to now flag 60% of our guild members, including at least 2 sub 60 level players. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
